# ======================================================================
# 🚀 DRILLING PIPELINE PRODUCTION CUSTOM RULES
# ======================================================================

# 1. Telemetry Datasets
# Prevents raw operational OSDU logs from cluttering the remote repository
*.csv

# 2. Database Layer Protection
# Ignores any structured database instance, temporary journal, or write-ahead log (WAL)
data_base/
database/
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
*.db-journal